cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.ET, cs.SY, cs.DS 

This paper deals with optimizing the word-line voltages for LDPC decoding in Flash memories, which involves information theory (cs.IT), circuit design (cs.AR), embedded systems (cs.ET), control systems (cs.SY), and data structures (cs.DS). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
